tspan.tspan: OpenBeta is an online climbing guide and
route finder by climbers, for climbers
OpenBeta was built by climbers that were frustrated with other online
climbing guides for the way they claim user data. Community and free
access is at the center of OpenBeta. It's open-source and the
information comes from the community of climbers who use it. The more
people that join and contribute, the better it gets for everyone!
